reviewText: The East side Kids a great series with good morale judgement. good guy vs bad guy and good wins. on time delivery and dependable provider

definitely a fan of all the dead end kids, east side, bowery boys movies. my low rating is for the lousy quality print, despite what other reviewers might say. it was a long time coming for the bowery boys dvd sets in great quality. i just hope it won't take much longer for the east side kids to be restored and released.

Hey dude! Wanna SEE whatcha watchin'? Wanna HEAR it too? Well, buy these collections from "Critics' Choice"! They's great! You can probably get 'em cheaper --- anywhere --- but NEVER as pristine as THESE suckers! WQow! Like being ON The Bowery! I can smell them fruits and vegetables, now!
